
THE GAME :

1 -> it 's the player;
9 -> it 's the second player

The player 1 can moove with the arrow keys.
Put a shield in front of him with the key M and get back his shield with the same key.
If the player press M in front of an enemy, it will kill the enemy and summon a heart to refiel his life.
The other player player moove with the keys Z Q S D and can summon monster with  the keys A and E.
The player one have to survive.
The second player can summon monsters to kill the first player.